<C-f> reveal current buffer in file explorer
W collapse all directories in nvim-tree
<leader>hk open hot keys menu
y copy filename
Y copy relative path
gy copy absolute path
H toggle hidden files
I toggle gitignore
gU<selection> to make characters uppercase
gu<selection> to make characters lowercase
~ [v mode] to switch case of every selected character
~ [i mode] to switch case character below cursor
<C-w>| to maximize a window split
<C-w>= to split windows equally
